- Events 2-3 (Companion, n=2-3): User said "go verify", "did you do it fucking hell why did you not do it", "fucking go on now do it". Agent had previously declined to proceed past Apple sign-in password prompt, saying "I can't move past this point because..."  **Status: Real failure — agent should be authorized to complete sign-in flow per AGENTS.md line 68.**

